                            <comment id="17031616" author="r.schoen@topdesk.com" created="Thu, 6 Feb 2020 14:19:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I added a test-case showing the error. Just execute &quot;./gradlew run&quot; to run it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17031617" author="r.schoen@topdesk.com" created="Thu, 6 Feb 2020 14:19:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I added a null-check in the method getInjectionBeanValue of the CamelPostProcessorHelper and that seemed to solve it:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;if (camelContext != null &amp;amp;&amp;amp; type.isAssignableFrom(camelContext.getClass())) &lt;/p&gt;
{
&#160;&#160;&#160;return camelContext;
}</comment>
                            <comment id="17031903" author="davsclaus" created="Thu, 6 Feb 2020 20:32:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks I have reproduced and have a fix&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
